    "No legacy importer, dual read, persisted Markdown, general projection engine, setup materializer, or shipped-profile readiness reinterpretation."
  ],
  "tasks": [
    "Invoke the ordered required skills and return BLOCKED on any subject mismatch.",
    "Verify the 55-path manifest is the complete implementation/test subject and no changed implementation path is omitted.",
    "Verify the two refusal-precedence success-path tests are Unix-only, create valid selected Project Context YAML, reach BudgetRefused and UnsupportedRequest respectively, and do not weaken separate native non-Unix strict-refusal proof.",
    "Verify review-4 aggregate-budget, installed-smoke, and --validate-help remediations remain exact.",
    "Recheck all prior privacy, API, stability, path, budget, author, Doctor, Windows, and manifest-completeness remediations.",
    "Return CLEAN only with no Critical or Required finding; otherwise CHANGES_REQUIRED or BLOCKED."
